comments: Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Harris (BKN) after Harris secures the loose ball.
Harris (PHI) places a hand/arm to the front of Dinwiddie (BKN) during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Dinwiddie (BKN) brings his right hand underneath the ball and brings it to a pause before continuing his dribble.
LAR shows Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact to the body of Dinwiddie (BKN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
RLB shows Harris (PHI) makes marginal contact with Allen (BKN) during the rebound.
Embiid (PHI) firms up and establishes himself in a screening position in the path of LeVert (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
LeVert (BKN) and Reddick (PHI) engage and disengage off ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Embiid (PHI) slides his pivot foot before the start of his dribble.
Embiid (PHI) initiates marginal contact with Allen (BKN) during his driving shot attempt that does not dislodge him from his defensive position.
Embiid (PHI) and Harris (BKN) make incidental contact with each other during the rebound.
Scott (PHI) and LeVert (BKN) make incidental contact with each other attempting to get to the loose ball.
Russell (BKN) makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) as Harris receives the throw-in.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
Simmons (PHI) makes some contact with Allen (BKN) but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Russell (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (PHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: The pass by Dinwiddie (BKN) is last touched by Russell (BKN) before going out of bounds.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Simmons (PHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact to the body of Harris (BKN) during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Scott (PHI) firms up on his right foot and establishes himself in a screening position in the path of LeVert (BKN) and does not deliver contact.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Allen (BKN) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass in the post.
Allen (BKN) firms up on his right foot and establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ennis III (PHI) and does not deliver contact.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Simmons (PHI) and does not deliver contact.
Harris (PHI) wraps his arm around Allen (BKN) during the pick and restricts his FOM.
RLS shows Simmons (PHI) makes marginal contact with Allen (BKN) before cleanly stealing the ball.
Harris (BKN) commits a take foul on Harris (PHI).
Allen (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Scott (PHI) and does not deliver contact.
